Mawethu,
UMongameli u-Oliver Reginald Tambo wayengutitshala wezibalo nezenzululwazi. Ke ngoko urhulumente uza kukhokelisa phambili izifundo zezibalo nezenzululwazi ngokumandla kulo nyaka, egameni lakhe.
